General Assembly Senate Joint
Resolution No. 6
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1723
Referred to Committee on JUDICIARY
Introduced by:
(JUD)
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE CLAIMS COMMISSIONER'S
COMPENSATION AWARD TO LUIS GALARZA WITH RESPECT TO
HIS CLAIM AGAINST THE STATE FOR WRONGFUL
INCARCERATION.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the decision of the Claims Commissioner, file number 27243 of
2 said commissioner, that compensation in the amount of $5,939,579.00,
3 payable from the adjudicated claims account of the General Fund, be
4 awarded to Luis Galarza with respect to his claim against the state for
5 wrongful incarceration, is confirmed.
LCO No. 1723 1 of 1

